Brute Force : T.C. - O(N), S.C. - O(N) 
My approach : I couldn't remember build in functions like isalnum(), reverse string function like (::-1) that made
me close to the answer but not to the code

class Solution:
    def isPalindrome(self, s: str) -> bool:
        newStr = ''
        for c in s:
            if c.isalnum():
                newStr += c.lower()
        return newStr == newStr[::-1]        
